      <note type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">No hands. Do not place hands in this area. Do not touch, lean on, or reach through the mast or permit others to do so.</p>
      </note>
      <fig class="- topic/fig ">
         <image href="media/image6.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image "/>
      </fig>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Located on the mast.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">No Standing On Forks Warning, No Standing Under Forks Warning</b>
      </p>
      <note type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Do not stand or ride on the forks. Do not stand or ride on a load or pallet on the forks.
        Do not stand or walk under the forks.</p>
      </note>
      <fig class="- topic/fig ">
         <image href="media/image7.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image "/>
      </fig>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Located on the lift cylinder.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Load Backrest Must Be In Place Warning</b>
      </p>
      <note type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
